videos.headline: Schor scampers for the TD
videos.description: JMU QB Schor easily walks in for the score.

videos.headline: Johnson breaks away for an  85 yd TD
videos.description: JMU's Cardon Johnson breaks into the second level scores the 85-yard score.

videos.headline: Robinson  rips the ball away for a pick in the endzone
videos.description: JMU's Rashad Robinson wrestles away the ball for the interception.

videos.headline: Sutton forces the fumble with a strip tackle
videos.description: Devon Sutton strips the ball away after the short completion to give ECU the ball.

videos.headline: Carlton hauls in the 17-yard TD
videos.description: Nick Carlton brings down the pass to give JMU a two-score lead.

videos.headline: Robinson puts the bow on the upset with the easy interception
videos.description: Rashad Robinson gets his second pick to ice the game for JMU.

videos.headline: Marshall adds to the blowout with a long TD run
videos.description: Marcus Marshall gets in on the fun with a 70-yard TD.

videos.headline: Breaking down JMU's season opening upset win
videos.description: It was a big day on the ground for the Dukes running backs.
